premise_source_doc_sentence: It was first sent to British contemporary hit radio on November 24 , 2016 , and it was released to US rhythmic contemporary radio on December 6 , 2016 through XO and Republic Records , serving as the album 's second single , following their previous collaboration `` Starboy '' .
It was released as the first single from the album on September 22 , 2016 , by XO and Republic Records .
